<DocsLayout title="CI/CD SDK" activeSection="sdk">
  <h1>CI/CD SDK</h1>
  <p>The SEO Crawler SDK is a standalone CLI binary that runs SEO/GEO checks in your CI/CD pipeline. Catch SEO regressions before they reach production.</p>

  <h2>Installation</h2>
  <h3>Build from source</h3>
  <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/booltools/booltools-seo-crawler.git
cd booltools-seo-crawler
make build-sdk
# Binary: bin/seo-crawler</code></pre>

